<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset='UTF-8' />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Account Created | Note Taking App</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      color: #232530; /* --color-system-neutral-800 */
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 32px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff; /* --color-system-neutral-0 */
      border-radius: 16px; /* --radius-16 */
      box-shadow: 0px 8px 12px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); /* --shadow-large */
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .header {
      background-color: #335cff; /* --color-system-blue-500 */
      padding: 32px; /* --spacing-400 */
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px; /* --text-preset-1 */
      line-height: 28.8px; /* --text-preset-1--line-height */
      letter-spacing: -0.5px; /* --text-preset-1--letter-spacing */
      font-weight: 700; /* --text-preset-1--font-weight */
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 32px; /* --spacing-400 */
    }
    
    .welcome-text {
      font-size: 20px; /* --text-preset-2 */
      line-height: 24px; /* --text-preset-2--line-height */
      letter-spacing: -0.5px; /* --text-preset-2--letter-spacing */
      font-weight: 700; /* --text-preset-2--font-weight */
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    p {
      font-size: 14px; /* --text-preset-4 */
      line-height: 16.8px; /* --text-preset-4--line-height */
      letter-spacing: -0.2px; /* --text-preset-4--letter-spacing */
      font-weight: 500; /* --text-preset-4--font-weight */
      color: #525866; /* --color-system-neutral-600 */
    }
    
    .email-address {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
      padding: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
      border-radius: 8px; /* --radius-8 */
      font-size: 16px; /* --text-preset-3 */
      font-weight: 600; /* --text-preset-3--font-weight */
      color: #232530; /* --color-system-neutral-800 */
      margin: 12px 0; /* --spacing-150 */
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #335cff; /* --color-system-blue-500 */
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px; /* --spacing-150 --spacing-300 */
      border-radius: 8px; /* --radius-8 */
      font-size: 16px; /* --text-preset-3 */
      font-weight: 600; /* --text-preset-3--font-weight */
      margin: 24px 0; /* --spacing-300 */
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #2547d0; /* --color-system-blue-700 */
    }
    
    .footer {
      padding: 24px 32px; /* --spacing-300 --spacing-400 */
      background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px; /* --text-preset-6 */
      line-height: 14.4px; /* --text-preset-6--line-height */
      color: #717784; /* --color-system-neutral-500 */
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e4ea; /* --color-system-neutral-200 */
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .email-container {
        margin: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
        border-radius: 12px; /* --radius-12 */
      }
      
      .header, 
      .content {
        padding: 24px; /* --spacing-300 */
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class='email-container'>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>Note Taking App</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class='content'>
      <h2 class="welcome-text">Your account has been created</h2>
      
      <p>Welcome to Note Taking App! Your account has been successfully created with the email address:</p>
      
      <div class="email-address">{{email}}</div>
      
      <p>You can now sign in to start organizing your thoughts and ideas:</p>
      
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href='{{loginUrl}}' class='btn'>Sign In to Your Account</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you didn't request this account, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class='footer'>
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</p>
      <p>Â© 2023 Note Taking App. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>